# CRITICAL: before cutover, inventory the current Wix site's ranking URLs from
# Google Search Console. Every old URL that ranks MUST resolve on the new site —
# either it exists at the same path, or it 301-redirects here. An old ranking URL
# that returns 404 is the one thing that actually kills rankings.
#
# Clean folder URLs (/contact/, /wedding-films/, etc.) are served automatically
# by Render from each folder's index.html — those don't need an entry here.
